                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 767.70/75.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-11-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 1, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Government has already taken certain steps for the safety of the city in
                    pursuance of the representations made by the Diplomatic Corps.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rockhill.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
